reviewText: This was the worse stand up ever. I only laughed one time during the whole dvd. If you watch it long enough you can see the audience trying to struggle to laugh at his boring performance. DO NOT WASTE YOUR TIME NOR MONEY ON THIS.

I can enjoy a bawdy comedian.  He goes a bit beyond bawdy and I think I might not have even cared if his material had just been funny.
Sadly, he has no real material of substance.

  Through out the performance my friends and I really hoped it was going to pick up momentum as well as finally inject some clever and original humor.
  It  never happened.

 I have seen a lot of comedy live and on video/tv/internet and this guy has to be one of the worse *so called comedians*.

I can only hope this was not one of his better performances.

I heard a clip of Smoove on the XM radio, comedy central channel. It cracked me up! When I got home for the night I searched on all my streaming video apps, and Amazon was the only one that had a full special of his stand up act. It was nothing like what I heard on the radio. Tired jokes about sex, and other things that just weren't appealing or funny. I chuckled a couple of times, but turned it off about two-thirds of the way through. I wish I could have heard more of the smoove act I heard on the radio...

JB Smoove's energy, fresh material and overall presence during his stand-up comedy act is an undeniable force. His love for his work comes through and is infectious. One of the best comics in the industry today!

I'm older... Jay Lenno show's too puerile for me. After watching this DVD I told my 31 yr old son to watch with his friends, to intrigue them with: "You aren't ready for this." Holy crap! Don't have to do crunches for awhile.
This one just doesn't do it for me. Not a fan of JB Smoove. Maybe I just don't get his comedy.

Very funny!  Lot's of new material.  Creative and imaginative story telling, puts you right in the middle of each situation to the point where you can actually see what JB's talking about.  Couldn't breathe from laughing so hard!
I have always been a fan. The theatrics that he performs while on stage really make the standup side splitting. Too funny.

I was very disappointed with this video. I enjoy JB in supporting roles on some sitcoms I've seen him in. When I saw this video was available I thought, well maybe his standup routine is good too. Boy, was I ever wrong. I could't even finish watching it to be honest.
Save your money....this one's a stinker.
This dvd was funny. JB is hilarious and his energy is uncontrollable. You will definitely laugh and be entertained.
Not as funny as I've seen him before.  Still amusing though.
it was funnier the first time i saw him perform
Too noisy and not really funny!
Very funny but I saw some of the material before from other comedians, that's why I give it a 4.
